      @ParameterizedTest @MethodSource("testCalculate") public void testCalculateParametrized​(Double value, char operator, Double initialValue, Double result) throws DivisionByZeroException, NotSupportedOperationException
      Method that tests method calculate from Calculator class. Tests valid inputs(without exceptions).
      Parameters:
      value - Value that will be added to currentValue, subtracted from currentValue, divided or multiplied by currentValue.
      operator - Operator used for testing calculate method.
      initialValue - Value used to set currentValue of Calculator before calling calculate method.
      result - Expected output of calculate method.
      Throws:
      DivisionByZeroException - Exception thrown if division by zero is performed.
      NotSupportedOperationException - Exception thrown if operation is not supported.
